docs.lead_paragraph: Women who have a history of dieting are more likely to experience excessive weight gain during pregnancy, a new study shows.

headline.main: Dieters Gain More Weight During Pregnancy

docs.abstract: Women who've spent much of their lives trying to lose weight appear to gain the most during pregnancy.
